# Generated by Cargo
# will have compiled files and executables
/target/

# Generated by Tauri
# will have schema files for capabilities auto-completion
/gen/schemas

# S13 (docs/design-explorations/s13-ios-blueprint.md, §D8) — `tauri ios init`
# generates gen/apple/ with its own .gitignore containing exactly these three
# entries; the lead commits the rest of gen/apple/ at integration (Xcode
# project, generated bindings, Assets.xcassets, Info.plist — it holds signing/
# capability/plist config that gets hand-edited), so only the per-machine
# build/derived-data pieces stay ignored here, matching the template's own
# list (raw.githubusercontent.com/tauri-apps/tauri/dev/crates/tauri-cli/
# templates/mobile/ios/.gitignore).
/gen/apple/xcuserdata/
/gen/apple/build/
/gen/apple/Externals/
